  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="6654860">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6654860/" class="title-link">万物源自比特</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6654860"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/freedxy/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2227740-5.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/freedxy/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">风撼斜阳</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-05-02"
      class="main-meta">2014-05-02 00:57:46</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6654860_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  我们每天都在接触无数的信息，它们如同洪流一般将我们淹没，很多时候让我们不知所措。那么信息究竟是什么？该如何来度量？它的过去和未来究竟是怎样的？我们可以从格雷克(James Gleick)的这本《信息简史》中略窥一二。  从非洲的鼓声到计算机中的电路，信息的载体经历了诸多的...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/6654860/#comments">(5回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">17有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
